quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  22,65,"Akuboni na ukuba uAllâh Wenze yaba ngaphantsi kwenu yonke into esemhlabeni neenqanawa zibaleka zinqumle ulwandle ngomyalelo waKhe? Kwanokuba Ubamba isibhakabhaka ukuba singawi phezu komhlaba, ngaphandle kwemvume yaKhe. Inene, uAllâh kubantu, Unobubele, nguSozinceba"
  22,66,"NguYe, Owaninika ubomi, noza kunenza nife, kwaye Usaya kuphinda Aninike ubomi kwakhona. Inene, umntu akanambulelo"
  22,67,Kwisizwe ngasinye Siyalele iinkonzo zenkolo amabazenze. Ngoko ke (wena Muhammad) bona (abangakholwayo) mabangaphikisani nawe ngombandela (lowo weenkonzo) koko bamemele eNkosini yakho. Inene wena useNdleleni ethe Tye
  22,68,"Ukuba bayaphikisana nawe ke, yithi: “UAllâh Wazi ngcono ngoko nikwenzayo.”"
  22,69,UAllâh Uza kugweba phakathi kwenu ngoMhla woVuko ngoko naniphikisana ngako
  22,70,"Akwazi na ukuba uAllâh Uyakwazi konke okusemazulwini nasemhlabeni? Inene, (konke) kuseNcwadini. Inene kulula oko kuAllâh"
  22,71,"Banqula ngaphandle koAllâh oko Angabathobelanga gunya ngako, noko bangenalwazi ngako; yaye kubenzi bobubi akuyi kubakho mncedi"
  22,72,"Ke kaloku xa iiVesi zeThu ezicacileyo zicengcelezwa kubo, uya kuphawula ukuziphika ebusweni babo bangakholwayo! Bona kukancinane nje ukuba basuke bahlasele ngobubhovubhovu babo abo bacengceleza iiVesi zeThu kubo. Yithi ke “Ndinganixelela ngeyona nto imbi kunene kunaleyo? NguMlilo (wesiHogo) lowo uAllâh Athembise ngawo kwabo bangakholwayo, asisesibi ngako eso siphelo sohambo.”"